Balsa E-Mail Client 0.4.9.5

Copyright (C) 1997-1999 Jay Painter and Stuart Parmenter
See 'COPYING' for licence information.


Please make sure you have the following things:

Glib       >= 1.2.1
GTK        >= 1.2.1
Imlib      >= 1.9.2
gnome-libs >= 1.0.8

If you do not have these, please check http://www.balsa.net/download.html for
links to these packages.

Build Instructions:

  * To compile:
    # ./configure
    # make

  * To install:
    # make install
